Class SampleClojureGamerStub

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Subject

    public final class SampleClojureGamerStub
extends ClojureGamer
    SampleClojureGamerStub is a stub that points to a version of @RandomGamer that has been implemented in Clojure. This stub needs to exist so that the Clojure code can interoperate with the rest of the Java framework (and applications like Kiosk and PlayerPanel as a result).
